snippet.title: PAC-MAN Museum + - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Let the nostalgia eat you up as you make your way through PAC-MAN Museum + with 14 of the series' legendary titles!

Play classic arcade PAC-MAN, Adventure in PAC-LAND, and even solve PAC-ATTACK puzzles.
Plus many more! Arriving Early 2022!
